            "type": "text",
            "text": "Brand Personality"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Pilot Mastery Academy carries the precision and authority of a flight instructor combined with the warmth of a mentor who was once a student pilot too. Technical rigor meets genuine encouragement. The brand communicates: 'We've flown this route. We'll get you there.'"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Voice & Tone"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "unordered-list",
